channel.name: BBC One NL
channel.title: Lost and Found in the Lakes
channel.desc: Our detectorists take on a search for a beloved ring lost on an old family farm for nearly half a century. Crafter Sally has a delivery of rubbish that we ask her to turn into items to be newly treasured, and can social media detective Mui solve the mystery of an old medal washed up on the beach and track down its owner.
